.sp
The Tizonia configuration file contains a block under the \fB[tizonia]\fP section
like the one pictured below (see also tizonia\-config\-label).
.sp
\fBWARNING:\fP
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
When user names and passwords are stored in your local
\fBtizonia.conf\fP, please ensure that this file has the correct
file system permissions to prevent other users from accessing your
credentials.
.sp
