.SH RASPBERRY PI
.sp
There are Tizonia binaries for Raspbian. All versions of Raspberry Pi are
supported. Select the \fBOMX.Aratelia.audio_renderer.alsa.pcm\fP renderer as the
default audio renderer in \fBtizonia.conf\fP\&.
.SS CONFIGURATION
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
